name: Tangle 03: Genuine
description: Drowning in sadness due to persistent problems will not make the problem pass quickly. Problems come not to make men down, but to restore the authenticity of men. That men do not have any power over anything, but the universe that will make all pass, and remember that help is very close. Become real men, who submit that we belong to the universe and all will return to it, then the men will get clues to the way out of the problem.
